uld be easy enough foe beginners.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">And Family BASIC.</div>
<br />How powerful is Family BASIC? Is it really possible to program a game with it? And I don't mean text games... I'm talking about games that are graphically nice, even if they are not very fast. And in order to make a standalone ROM, would you have to rip the interpreter and pack it along with your game?</div>

